b31802aa3e1fee839a08de25f97917c0  l/libarchive-3.2.1-x86_64-1.txz


Installation instructions:
+------------------------+

Upgrade the package as root:
# upgradepkg libarchive-3.2.1-i486-1_slack14.1.txz


